            &none         &none         &none         &none         &none           &none      &kp F4    &kp F5      &kp F6  &kp F11
&bt BT_CLR  &none         &none         &none         &none         &none           &none      &kp F1    &kp F2      &kp F3  &kp F12  &none
                                        &none         &kp TAB       &kp SPACE       &kp ENTER  &kp BSPC  &kp DELETE
            >;
